# Cross-origin isolation → enables SharedArrayBuffer → onnxruntime-web uses
# multiple WASM threads (2-4x faster CPU inference, esp. on phones).
# The app is fully same-origin; model/ort/tess responses carry CORP too.
/*
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: require-corp
  Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: cross-origin
